What's wrong?

99
00:06:23,900 --> 00:06:24,300
This...

100
00:06:24,460 --> 00:06:25,220
How could it be peaches?

101
00:06:25,260 --> 00:06:26,700
Yeah.

102
00:06:26,820 --> 00:06:28,180
