112
00:06:48,700 --> 00:06:50,380
my father will blame me with a glare.

113
00:06:50,700 --> 00:06:52,300
What about having a banquet

114
00:06:52,540 --> 00:06:54,700
to enjoy the peaches together?

115
00:06:57,420 --> 00:06:58,980
You can share the peaches.

116
00:06:59,220 --> 00:07:00,940
