117
00:07:02,660 --> 00:07:04,420
Thanks to Princess Jiuge, we can enjoy peaches.

118
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:07,140
What... What...

119
00:07:09,540 --> 00:07:11,420
What's wrong?

120
00:07:11,540 --> 00:07:12,140
Yeah.

121
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:13,140
How could the prize become peaches?

122
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:34,260
Why did His Majesty

123
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:36,980
use a basket of flat peaches

124
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:38,420
to change the pimpon fruit?

125
00:07:40,700 --> 00:07:41,380
He clearly knows

126
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:43,100
how eager I am to get the fruit.

127
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:46,300
In order to get the fruit,

128
00:07:46,300 --> 00:07:48,300
how diligent and attentive I am! He knows it.

129
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:52,540
Why did he change it?

130
00:07:59,180 --> 00:08:00,540
Even at this time,

131
00:08:01,860 --> 00:08:03,700
