132
00:08:10,060 --> 00:08:11,140
Princess Jiuge.

133
00:08:12,580 --> 00:08:13,700
Please wait a moment.

134
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:20,660
The master is not here.

135
00:08:21,340 --> 00:08:22,460
I specially come to look for you

136
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:24,700
behind his back.

137
00:08:26,220 --> 00:08:26,900
Actually,

138
00:08:29,660 --> 00:08:31,460
I always want to get

139
00:08:31,700 --> 00:08:33,100
the pimpon fruit near the Jieyou Spring as well.

140
00:08:34,020 --> 00:08:34,900
So

141
00:08:36,500 --> 00:08:39,140
I specially went to ask master for it the night before.

142
00:08:39,700 --> 00:08:42,420
Unexpectedly, master asked His Highness Lian Song

143
00:08:42,700 --> 00:08:44,340
to bring a basket of flat peaches

144
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:47,500
to change the pimpon fruit from Her Majesty and gave it to me.

145
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:48,580
I know

146
00:08:48,980 --> 00:08:51,980
you took part in the competition
in order to get the pimpon fruit.

147
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:54,580
Thinking twice,

148
00:08:54,980 --> 00:08:56,700
I think I should tell you the truth.

149
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:58,500
So

150
00:09:00,060 --> 00:09:00,860
before the competition,

151
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:03,140
you knew we couldn't get the pimpon fruit, right?

152
00:09:05,820 --> 00:09:06,740
Yeah.

153
00:09:09,980 --> 00:09:10,780
Then

154
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:15,140
would you like to

155
00:09:15,740 --> 00:09:17,140
share half of your pimpon fruit with me?

156
00:09:17,420 --> 00:09:18,820
I can give you anything you want in exchange for it.

157
00:09:19,060 --> 00:09:20,860
The purpose of my special coming

158
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:22,660
is to let you know that

159
00:09:23,060 --> 00:09:26,660
I won't share the pimpon fruit with you.

160
00:09:31,420 --> 00:09:33,940
Besides, I still have an unreasonable demand.

161
00:09:34,780 --> 00:09:35,620
From now on,

162
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:39,180
please keep away from the master.

163
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:41,220
I don't know

164
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:42,940
why you tell me such words.

165
00:09:44,100 --> 00:09:45,020
Since you

166
00:09:45,580 --> 00:09:47,500
wouldn't like to share the pimpon fruit with me,

167
00:09:48,620 --> 00:09:50,220
I have nothing to say with you.

168
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:50,980
I know

169
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:52,940
after hearing my words,

170
00:09:53,180 --> 00:09:55,140
you must be very unhappy.

171
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:57,100
But what I did is good for you.

172
00:09:57,460 --> 00:10:00,580
These days, master paid special regard to you.

173
00:10:00,820 --> 00:10:02,060
Maybe in your heart,

174
00:10:02,260 --> 00:10:03,780
it's not as peaceful as before.

175
00:10:06,300 --> 00:10:08,220
Master has lived for tens of thousands of years

176
00:10:09,060 --> 00:10:10,380
with immortal longevity.

177
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:12,660
It's hard for him to avoid feeling lonely.

178
00:10:13,020 --> 00:10:14,340
He also loves new and fresh things.

179
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:16,460
Princess Jiuge.

180
00:10:17,460 --> 00:10:19,100
It's true that you are clever and beautiful.

181
00:10:19,820 --> 00:10:22,060
Maybe the master is interested in you with favor,

182
00:10:22,300 --> 00:10:24,220
which is also reasonable.

183
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:28,140
But he just regards you as

184
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:30,380
a fresh playmate different from those in the past.

185
00:10:30,660 --> 00:10:32,460
If you deeply lose yourself in it,

186
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:34,500
it can only make you sad.

187
00:10:37,660 --> 00:10:38,740
I knew it.

188
00:10:41,860 --> 00:10:43,500
I understood it very early.

189
00:10:56,820 --> 00:10:58,140
In order to get the pimpon fruit,

190
00:10:58,340 --> 00:10:59,300
I have worked very hard

191
00:10:59,540 --> 00:11:01,140
and suffered a lot.

192
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:03,660
But it's nothing compared with

193
00:11:03,780 --> 00:11:05,700
Ji Heng's simple words in front of His Majesty.

194
00:11:06,660 --> 00:11:07,980
To spoil Ji Heng,

195
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:10,980
His Majesty still has many other precious things to give her.

196
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:13,500
But Ye Qingti can only be saved

197
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:15,660
by the pimpon fruit.

198
00:11:16,260 --> 00:11:17,700
These days,

199
00:11:18,340 --> 00:11:19,700
even if His Majesty just regards me

200
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:21,540
as a new playmate for fun,

201
00:11:22,420 --> 00:11:25,260
I think I am a competent playmate.

202
00:11:25,940 --> 00:11:27,980
If he'd like to give me some of the fruit,

203
00:11:28,060 --> 00:11:30,380
I can still be his playmate.

204
00:11:31,020 --> 00:11:32,540
Whatever he asks me to do,

205
00:11:32,980 --> 00:11:34,780
I will do it.

206
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:46,940
Third Prince.

207
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:06,180
Third Prince, what do you mean?

208
00:12:07,460 --> 00:12:08,340
Si Ming.

209
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:10,100
I heard you're not good at drinking alcohol.

210
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:13,380
Once you drink some alcohol, you can't help talking randomly.

211
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:18,100
Indeed I have such a defect.

212
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:21,980
I know you have some secret sorrow.

213
00:12:22,540 --> 00:12:23,140
What about

214
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:24,700
letting you drink alcohol

215
00:12:25,740 --> 00:12:28,100
and tell the truth after you are drunk?

216
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:30,340
Then I will know what I want to know

217
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:33,820
and you won't feel guilty about the secret that you have to keep.

218
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:34,580
Right?

219
00:12:34,940 --> 00:12:35,900
Secret?

220
00:12:37,340 --> 00:12:39,940
What you want to know is the things between Her Highness Fengjiu

221
00:12:40,140 --> 00:12:41,620
and His Majesty, right?

222
00:12:49,180 --> 00:12:52,940
I used to think Her Highness
and His Majesty are not destined to be together.

223
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:55,940
Taking the Prestige of Qingqiu and Fengji into account of,

224
00:12:56,140 --> 00:12:57,380
I hide everything,

225
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:58,820
