229
00:13:07,300 --> 00:13:08,740
What do you still care about?

230
00:13:28,220 --> 00:13:31,580
It began when Fengjiu hid her identity,

231
00:13:31,740 --> 00:13:34,780
coming to Tai Chen Palace to be a fairy maid.

232
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:53,620
Is His Majesty in?

233
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:55,180
No, he isn't.

234
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:56,900
You're late for a moment.

235
00:13:57,220 --> 00:13:58,100
He has just left.

236
00:13:58,580 --> 00:14:00,700
Ji Heng held an injured spiritual fox to turn to him.

237
00:14:01,060 --> 00:14:02,660
He first input some immortal power to the spiritual fox

238
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:04,060
to save its life,

239
00:14:04,300 --> 00:14:05,260
fed it an elixir next

240
00:14:05,500 --> 00:14:06,980
and then took it to the Sky Kingdom.

241
00:14:07,820 --> 00:14:09,980
I heard it was a little like

242
00:14:10,140 --> 00:14:11,580
the fox he lost that very year,

243
00:14:11,860 --> 00:14:13,380
so he showed great mercy,

244
00:14:14,140 --> 00:14:15,940
which made Ji Heng deeply moved.

245
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:17,940
Had it not been for Ji Heng's lack of enough cultivation
to leave the valley,

246
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:19,540
I'm afraid she would have gone with him to the Sky Kingdom.

247
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,940
Ji Heng went to see ice face off.

248
00:14:23,300 --> 00:14:24,580
I don't want to see him,

249
00:14:25,020 --> 00:14:25,980
so I'm here to wait for your return.

250
00:14:26,220 --> 00:14:27,140
And bring you out for a drink.

251
00:14:28,660 --> 00:14:31,260
Ji Heng held a little fox to turn to him.

252
00:14:33,900 --> 00:14:34,620
In my view,

253
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:37,260
ice face won't be back in three or four days.

254
00:14:37,540 --> 00:14:38,620
Do you have something urgent to see him?

255
00:14:40,060 --> 00:14:42,620
You said His Majesty couldn't be back
in three or four days, right?

256
00:14:43,980 --> 00:14:45,740
