264
00:15:03,100 --> 00:15:03,540
Ji Heng just...

265
00:15:03,620 --> 00:15:04,260
Yan.

266
00:15:07,380 --> 00:15:08,620
Are you OK?

267
00:15:08,860 --> 00:15:10,780
Let's drink till all is blue.

268
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,340
Have a drink another day.

269
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:42,340
Ye Qingti.

270
00:15:43,500 --> 00:15:45,420
Since I have promised you,

271
00:15:49,020 --> 00:15:50,900
